title: Tech baseball upended in series finale at ETSU, 11-3 - Tennessee Tech
content: Tech baseball upended in series finale at ETSU, 11-3  Tennessee Tech
description: JOHNSON CITY, Tenn. â€“ In its finale with ETSU, the Tennessee Tech baseball team could not pull off the weekend sweep, falling to the Buccaneers at Thomas Stadium by a final score of 11-3 in the first-ever three-game series between the two in-state rivals.
